A fork of http://github.com/asynclabs/WiShield with changes to fix
the following issues related to it being developed prior to Arduino 1.0:
- Unknown data type error: prog_char and prog_uchar.
- File not found error: wiring.h and WProgram.h.
- Incorrect return type error: write().

Tested with:
- Arduino IDE 1.0.1
- Custom Arduino (ATmega 328)
- Microchip MRF24WB0MA WiFi Transceiver
- Mac OS 10.8.2
